places.name: Nedumangad Town Juma Masjid.
places.address: J232+9MX Nedumangad Town Juma Masjid., SH3, Pazhavadi, Nedumangad, Kerala 695541

featured_reviews.review_id: Juma mosque at the heart of the town. 3 floors can accommodate about 700 people. Toilets are below average. About 50 pipes, 2 howz and one old well are there for taking wudu. Only 30 bikes can park in the mosque premises; cars needed to be parked in the roadside. A small store is there for selling Islamic books, praying materials and dry fruits. One generator for uninterrupted power supply. Madrasas are held in the next block which is just average only. High quality carpets are laid. Most modern Ahuja audio systems and lightings are there. Imam's chamber is decorated with beautiful calligraphic works. Sufficient fans and clocks are there. This all makes it a convenient mosque in Nedumangadu to offer namaz.
